    "In addition, the diffusion model is also applied to Image Rectangling (Zhou et al. 2024), Image Segmentation (Baranchuk et al. 2022; et al. 2023), Semantic Matching (Li et al. 2024), Visual Emotion Analysis (Yang et al. 2024), Face Recognition (Boutros et al. 2023), Anomaly Detection (Zhang et al. 2023), etc.",
    "As technology progresses, it is imperative to contemplate the harmonization of artistic innovation with ethical responsibility.",
